title: The Deadly Basement of a 4chan Doomer (Documentary)

media:group.media:title: The Deadly Basement of a 4chan Doomer (Documentary)
media:group.media:description:
In 2017 the home of a reclusive multimillionaire was set ablaze. Inside firefighters discovered deplorable hoarding conditions, the charred body of a young man, and a secret tunnel system sprawling 200 ft underground. One year later the owner of the home, Daniel Beckwitt, was charged and convicted of 2nd degree Depraved Heart Murder.
